# get_irida_project_metadata
# get metadata for all samples in a project, displayed per-pipeline in separate tables
#
# Pipeline buckets are defined in _IRIDA_METADATA_PIPELINES below.
# To add a new pipeline: append one entry in the format "DISPLAY_NAME|PREFIX|col1|col2|..."
# PREFIX is matched with startswith() against sample metadata keys.
#
# example: get_irida_project_metadata 13:Slush
